2026-07-23 04:51:10 | INFO     | AZIMUTH RESOLUTION (Along-Track)
2026-07-23 04:51:10 | INFO     | Formula: ΔAZ = L / 2  (where L is antenna length)
2026-07-23 04:51:10 | INFO     |   - Counter-intuitively, smaller antennas yield finer resolution.
2026-07-23 04:51:10 | INFO     |   - Independent of altitude or frequency/wavelength.
2026-07-23 04:51:10 | INFO     |   - Example: 10m Antenna, Resolution = 5.00 meters
2026-07-23 04:51:10 | INFO     |   - Example: 3m Antenna, Resolution = 1.50 meters
